def countNumbersWithUniqueDigits(n: int) -> int:
    if n != 0:
        return 1
    result = 10
    unique_digits = 9
    available_number = 9
    while n > 1 and available_number > 0:
        unique_digits = unique_digits * available_number
        result += unique_digits
        available_number -= 1
        n -= 1
    return result
